EDA/Cleaning: Figures are too small to read.
Finding 1: the last bit regarding reason CT was administered is quite interesting!
Finding 2: A regular correlation analysis is rather simple - perhaps this would fit better in the EDA section.
Reality check: cannot use other publications as your reality check without citing them.
Stability check: Go a bit deeper - how does this change if we repeat this over and over again? Why is a drop of 10% of the data at random a good stability analysis? Needs more defense.
